# MLSECDEVOPS GitLab Pipeline CI -- data quality / drift group.
# Each of these installs in its own per-job venv (great-expectations-validate,
# evidently-drift, ydata-profile, dvc-verify); ydata-profiling in particular pins
# narrow numpy/pandas/matplotlib ranges. If this group cannot resolve as one lock,
# the lockfile-audit job reports a WARNING and these stay covered by the per-job
# .audit-env. See requirements-ci.in for the grouping rationale.
great-expectations
evidently
ydata-profiling
dvc[all]
